{"tid":1394445,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長實：社會事件對售樓有影響","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T12:18:16.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1afdf4495ba094bb2a0836a09b3a68d43256410b","tid":1394445,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:57:44.000Z","msg":"近月社會因修訂《逃犯條例》發生連串示威及衝突事件，長實集團(01113)主席李澤鉅在分析員會議上表示，近期事件對售樓有一定影響，因為市民若非必要不會貿然入市，但相信市場對細價樓仍有逼切需求。<br />\n<br />\n李澤鉅續稱，事件對旗下酒店業務影響不大，因為附屬酒店並非位處中環區，在「佔中」期間亦沒有帶來影響，認為此類社會事件只屬短期性。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他指出，集團會繼續留意在內地的投資機會，強調並沒有特別偏好任何一個國家。至於英國脫歐方區，最大的危機是會影響貨幣滙率。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2207806/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2207806%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEVQKcmgIyYy1b1J%2Bn%2Bjwg5M%3D&h=0fb51dd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2207806/</a>"},{"pid":"50a644c505990ed05d438d06151c6611ef86d183","tid":1394445,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8134a9b3f9dc3702cde8484278b4681882edd84d","tid":1394445,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"b06e2c7a98ddda4217b1424192bd466d1c7be632","tid":1394445,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:18:16.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好賣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}